show.description: Meera, a mistreated maid, discovers she’s the real heiress of the powerful Kapoor family. Stripped of identity and dignity by the cruel Rhea, who falsely claims her place, Meera is cast out, humiliated, and betrayed. But she rises from the ashes as Phoenix, a mysterious designer set on reclaiming her name. While Rhea clings to stolen power through lies and manipulation, Meera begins a quiet, calculated revenge. Secrets unravel, loyalties shift, and the battle between truth and deception erupts — as Meera transforms from victim to vengeance, ready to take back everything that was once hers. To know in detail watch out " Revenge Of The Heiress"
